        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis change was tested locally:\n\nWhen tests are not skipped, everything builds and the tests run, when tests are skipped, everything builds but no tests are run.\n\nThe dependency on clamp-common and clamp-models and the build is outside the profiles so it is always included. The when tests are not skipped, the other dependency on clamp-common-tests is dragged in.\n\nDuring local testing the clamp-common-tests jar in the local .m2 was deleted. When tests were skipped, the dependency was not downloaded, when tests are run, the dependency was downloaded.",
